Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:12.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}朧雲に放て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:14.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}信じる道は
