Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}入侵者？怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}似乎没被人动过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻…麻痹弹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}超秘传忍法书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被偷走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自从那次奇袭之后就加强了警备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能够侵入学院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}并且打开保险库的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}连同我在内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就只有在场的诸位了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们不可能做那种事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是忍法书被盗也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那…究竟是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总之 我要先联络本部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天大家就在自己房间待命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在房间里待命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}该做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然是要念书么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}超秘传忍法书…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这…怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么会在这
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然遵守诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成为我的好朋友了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}求你了 请放过小柳生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看在可爱的云雀如此勇气可嘉的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就放她一马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}与此相对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要成为我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 这就是朋友间的信物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是位可爱的人偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这下你就背叛了半藏学院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是背叛了全部善忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正你也会被当成拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我发现了你那卓越的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打从见到你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那软弱外表下的谨慎和敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无比适合间谍的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者不单单是肉体上的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你这样的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们可是相当看好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要我转…转校么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果你愿意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我期待着你的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}俺在想什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:05:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小云雀她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我来还书时看到这封信在这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀同学竟然会是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别叫她犯人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她不是写着她只是受蛇女子学园的恶忍控制了才那么做的么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是…究竟是怎么做到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是这个么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}念力发射器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}念力发射器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是可以接收经过特殊训练的忍者的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}并增幅的忍具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}经过增幅的意念波动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能够自由操纵被控者的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是傀儡使常用的一手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}究竟是什么时候做的手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全都是云雀的错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管我怎么道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我都犯下了无可饶恕的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我一定会拿回忍法书
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算是拼上这条性命去换
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}柳生！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\blur8}忍·转身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\blur8}忍·转身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}俺要去找云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可你根本不知道她去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道俺也一定要找
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太乱来了 小柳生！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要妨碍我！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有 学院那边没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一碰到云雀的事就什么都不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}绕到背后了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}冷静点 小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:07:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别管俺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}柳生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原来在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是俺的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其实我知道 昨晚云雀不在房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听说入侵者的事情的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但要俺去怀疑云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}俺做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那不是理所当然的么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果换成是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀被操控这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谁也没发现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不单是这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}补习之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}俺丢下云雀独自回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果俺一直陪着她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也不会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都是俺的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是的 小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这绝不是小柳生的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}错的不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而是操控了云雀让她做了这种事的蛇女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}硬要说有责任的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我们每个人都脱不了关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}柳生同学 你忘了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们可是“伙伴”呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伙伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家一样都很担心云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不单单是小柳生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}应该就在这前面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}秘立蛇女子学园
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可疑的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是善忍的间谍么！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}让我见春花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}竟然要见春花大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}春花大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抓到了一个窥视学园的可疑女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她说要见春花大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊呀 来得还真是意外的快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}带她来我房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是按规定抓到入侵者时要先向学园报告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我说的是 带她来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很抱歉 立刻去办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这绑法是何等粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}毫无情调可言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不好意思 我们学校的学生都这么粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}弄得那么脏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我刚刚正好也在沐浴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看来你是听明白了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我真高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半藏学院已经没有我的容身之所了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但曾是半藏学院出身的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的能加入蛇女学园么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们绝不会加害你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把自己交给我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}主人的秘密指令根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只不过是想要这孩子罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定要把忍法书拿回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里是训练场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛇女学园通过恶忍雄厚的财力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在全日本物色有潜能的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正因如此 平庸之辈数量也不少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这还真是位稀客呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我还以为是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这不是半藏学院的忍者嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}担任警卫的人真该受罚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她从今天起就是蛇女子学园的学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我引荐来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}春花姐的坏习惯又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是认真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为我已经回不去半藏学院了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那从现在开始你就是我们的伙伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}“怎么了”是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道你不怀疑云雀么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怀疑什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太过轻易地接纳曾经的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是这么想的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所谓善
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既狭隘又充满歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恶比善更为宽容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就是善忍和恶忍的区别
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是云雀背叛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}确实 背叛过一次的人难保不会背叛第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有本事背叛我们就放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恶来者不拒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但一切都要自己负责
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敢无视我就杀了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果不无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就和你普通交个朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}中产阶级么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人畜无害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你喜欢豆芽菜么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}豆芽菜啊豆芽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 不讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那你对于最近豆芽菜涨价怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我觉得难以令人饶恕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本是庶民之友的豆芽菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}帮大忙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有人来听她说豆芽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:24.25,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}整整涨了2元啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}差不多是修行的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍字心上一把刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在心里要有一把利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有…我是惊讶有这么多学生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半藏学院只有五个学生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恶忍没有善忍那般在乎血统
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了逃避世人的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有各种各样入学的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小焰她原本也是善忍的家系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本该成为你们的同学才是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那为什么当了恶忍？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想你肯定也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半藏学院这样的善忍学校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只招收过去没有违法行为的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}违法行为？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听说她刺过他人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她只能选择当恶忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未来过去好像很受欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她为了向世间的一切进行复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才踏上了恶忍的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小日影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从小就在战场上长大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不得已成为了战斗机器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在贫民街长大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}父母由于贫困而双亡的小咏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}则是憎恨这社会结构本身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在这蛇女子学园依靠自己的实力一步步爬上来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是我们五个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}与你们从前提条件就不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}与你们从前提条件就不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这位是铃音老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们的教官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从半藏学院倒戈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真让人难以置信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}并不是没有前例
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}通过倒戈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也有可能成为了更加优秀的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}春香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是叫云雀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从善忍变成恶忍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是需要觉悟的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甚至需要你抛弃身心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身…心么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}铃音老师曾经也是善忍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是最高机密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}告诉你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是为了让你知道也有像你这样的人存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这种感觉是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 刚才好像想到了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}转学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这种时候么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是学生的推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以认同她作为忍者的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是那名学生…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}管理学生是你的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什么不满么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对于我没通知你便独断夺取这东西这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我之前也跟您说过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仅仅夺取它毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只不过是个愚蠢的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我希望搞清楚 铃音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你以为你是靠谁才能待在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:18:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我把曾为善忍 在任务中垂死的你带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}并且将你提拔至今的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一直铭记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总在利用我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最终获得今天的地位的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不正是你么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看来已经不容踌躇了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是时候将这月色染上一抹血红了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛇女以拥有大量的学生为傲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}考虑到要掩人耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}应该不会像半藏学院这样隐身于都市
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是远离尘世的小岛还是深山的山凹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}方位也是个疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}毕竟是忍者设施
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恐怕还考虑到了气学和风水的因素
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好复杂实在跟不上呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}似乎冷静下来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是该对我道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}若不是飞鸟找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:18:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个时候的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}脑子里一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一点也没有手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟她避开了我动真格的一击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那一击就连蛇女的恶忍也未曾躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是说 飞鸟的身手飞跃性的成长了么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拥有相当的潜力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽说她自身尚未意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}潜藏的强大即为无意中的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}故为双刃之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但若走错一步…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}双刃剑么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想起了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在我回来之前全体待命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:20:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了 葛城姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}平常他不都是一阵烟雾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}“嘭”的消失么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}声音是从这附近传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛇女子学园
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍术讲师 铃音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}铃音？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半藏学院
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者科教师 雾夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来与我交手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}故意将刀法展示给我看么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看到您的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就忍不住想要试试
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:21:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没想到仅仅一击就暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不愧是我的师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我怎么会忘记自己学生的刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说到学生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的学生寄名到了蛇女门下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀果然去了蛇女么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你我现在都是负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以通知你一声才合乎礼节
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么你要成为恶忍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.15,0:21:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我会在那里告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛇女的地图…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.93,0:21:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我等着你 雾夜老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}凛！
Comment: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\blur5}ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:12.94,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}捧げた思いが冷えたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:19.25,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}氷の乙女になるんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:25.98,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}信じた願いが朽ちたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:33.22,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}戦う乙女になるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.59,0:22:39.93,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}あどけないと言われた頃に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:46.61,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}戻れないから　この身はさまよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:49.56,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}孤独の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:53.48,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}暗夜の悪しき者よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:56.80,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}誇り高く麗しく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:23:00.24,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}こころに香る花は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:03.46,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}震えまいと空に咲く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:06.86,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}暗夜の悪しき者よ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:10.30,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}誇り高く麗しく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:13.60,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}こころは赤い花よ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:17.07,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}摘み取られる前に散れ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:12.94,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}若是奉上的思念渐渐冷却
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:19.25,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我会变成一位庞若寒冰的女孩么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:25.98,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}若是坚信的愿望枯萎腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:33.22,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我会变成一位沉沦战斗的女孩么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.59,0:22:39.93,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}那段被人称作“天真无邪”的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:46.61,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}已经回不来了 所以我的肉身才会在此彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:49.56,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在这孤独之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:53.48,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}暗夜的邪恶之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:56.80,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}有我们的美学与荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:23:00.24,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在心中芬香的花朵儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:03.46,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不惧颤抖要在空中绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:06.86,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}暗夜的邪恶之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:10.30,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}有我们的美学与荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:13.60,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}心中那朵赤红的花儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:17.07,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}定要在被人摘取前凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}春花大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.45,0:23:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又有人无视我真火大！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其实我有种让你万众瞩目的忍法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全裸戴着火男面具跳草裙舞就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.25,0:23:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就会成为众人的焦点咯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早知道就不该问你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下一集 阴与阳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拼上性命来相夺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:39.97,Chapter,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,484)\bord2\blur2\shad1\c&HE2EEEE&\3c&H383A3B&}阴与阳